                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've got 23 wins in MM so far.  I've gone and talked to Vual Stoutest in the Butcherblock adventure camp so far.  I've learned all sorts of good information, and it says that my adventurer's stoen gains in power.   
<br />

