After reading your post, I ran to Henai Silentwalker in Dagnors Cauldron.  After hailing him, he tells me I need to go adventure more.  I'm wondering, do I need 15 more wins without talking to anyone and then go back to Henai?</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
